content: mbcse: Merged two significant PRs this week: #1950 adding a Local Embedding Manager to reuse local embedding models (+7833/-1143 lines) and #1876 implementing a Twitter post approval mechanism via Discord bot (+404/-27 lines). Currently has an open PR (#2025) addressing character file plugins import errors, with substantial code modifications across nearly 2000 files (+126k/-58k lines) primarily focused on bug fixes (73%).
